parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "Mesonh",
  "software": [
    "PrepPgd",
    "PrepNest",
    "PrepReal",
    "Spawning",
    "Mesonh",
    "Diag",
    "Conv2dia",
    "Diaprog"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "cpu": {
      "cores": "${NBP}",
      "time": "${TIME}"
    },
    "memory": "${MEM}"
  },
  "file_transfer": {
    "input": {
      "protocol": "ssh" if "${INHOST}" == "*'@'*" else "local",
      "remote_path": "${INHOST}:${INDIR}" if "${INHOST}" == "*'@'*" else "${INDIR}"
    },
    "output": {
      "protocol": "ssh" if "${OUTHOST}" == "*'@'*" else "local",
      "remote_path": "${OUTHOST}:${OUTDIR}" if "${OUTHOST}" == "*'@'*" else "${OUTDIR}"
    }
  },
  "job_scheduler": "PBS",
  "job_type": "multi" if "${JOBMULTI}" else "mono",
  "environment_variables": {
    "NBP": "number of processors",
    "TIME": "maximum execution time",
    "MNH_EXP": "experiment name",
    "CAT": "command for concatenating files",
    "SUBDIR": "subdirectory for execution",
    "EXECDIR": "execution directory",
    "LINKFILES": "command for creating symbolic links",
    "INDIR": "input directory",
    "OUTDIR": "output directory",
    "GETFILES": "command for getting files",
    "RMINDIR": "command for removing input directory",
    "OUTHOST": "output host",
    "PUTFILES": "command for putting files",
    "RMMKDIR": "command for creating output directory",
    "RMOUTDIR": "command for removing output directory",
    "RMSHELL": "command for running shell commands",
    "JOBMULTI": "job header for multi-processor jobs",
    "JOBMONO": "job header for single-processor jobs",
    "PREP_PGD_FILES": "directory for PREP_PGD files",
    "OUT_CPGDFILE": "output CPGD file",
    "INP_CPGDFILE_FATHER": "input CPGD file for father domain",
    "INP_YPGD1": "input YPGD file for level 1",
    "INP_YPGD2": "input YPGD file for level 2",
    "INP_YPGD3": "input YPGD file for level 3",
    "INP_YPGD4": "input YPGD file for level 4",
    "LISTGET": "list of files to get",
    "CRT_YNEST": "command for creating YNEST file",
    "OUT_YPGD1_NEST": "output YPGD file for level 1 (nested)",
    "OUT_YPGD2_NEST": "output YPGD file for level 2 (nested)",
    "LISTE_PUT": "list of files to put",
    "INDIR_HATMFILE": "input directory for HATMF file",
    "INP_HATMFILE": "input HATMF file",
    "SUF": "suffix for HATMF file",
    "INP_HPGDFILE": "input HPGD file",
    "INP_CFILE": "input CFILE file",
    "OUT_CINIFILE": "output CINIFILE file",
    "INP_YDOMAIN": "input YDOMAIN file",
    "INP_CINIFILE": "input CINIFILE file",
    "OUT_CINIFILE_SPA": "output CINIFILE file (spawning)",
    "INP_CINIFILE1": "input CINIFILE file 1",
    "INP_CINIFILE2": "input CINIFILE file 2",
    "CRT_CEXP": "command for creating CEXP file",
    "CRT_CSEG": "command for creating CSEG file",
    "OUT_XFMOUT": "output XFMOUT file",
    "INP_YINIFILE": "input YINIFILE file",
    "CRT_YSUFFIX": "command for creating YSUFFIX file",
    "OUT_DIAG": "output DIAG file",
    "CRT_CVYSUFFIX": "command for creating CVYSUFFIX file",
    "OUT_CVFILE": "output CVFILE file",
    "INP_FILE1": "input FILE1 file",
    "NOVISU": "flag for disabling visualization",
    "OUT_GMFILE": "output GMFILE file"
  }
}
```
